Clone with HTTPS
# git clone https://github.com/27kanth/concerto_staging.git

# docker ps -a              >> shows all running and stopped containers
# docker-compose up -d      >> starts the container from background
# docker ps                 >> only running containers
# docker-compose ps         >> only docker compose containers status

